{"tid":655494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★調查指寮屋劏房戶人均居住面積 較獨立囚室細","createTime":"2018-05-06T14:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T09:09:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ed03b7bb593faf7589477ec932889487f03a38","tid":655494,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/222142_224927cb78567d99ff7b3605014d9899.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F222142_224927cb78567d99ff7b3605014d9899.PNG&h=2cf39f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/222143_e507a60315ffcec3206a2580370d5a8a.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F222143_e507a60315ffcec3206a2580370d5a8a.PNG&h=a9c3641f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/222144_6a2366e0cf332af99b9ad7bf81e922bd.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F222144_6a2366e0cf332af99b9ad7bf81e922bd.PNG&h=df39cb69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/222145_f434207c8f9e73f70f369522168e9733.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F222145_f434207c8f9e73f70f369522168e9733.PNG&h=42c29910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/222146_ea5af2452e2fb0d9000630c4042a1744.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F222146_ea5af2452e2fb0d9000630c4042a1744.PNG&h=7d6c5e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一項調查顯示，近八成受訪寮屋住戶，居住單位面積不足二百平方呎，其中寮屋劏房戶人均居住面積更<span style=\"color: red;\">比監獄的獨立囚室細</span>。<br />\n<br />\n63歲的梁先生住在粉嶺寮屋區，一個大約五十平方呎的劏房，月租二千五百元，平日他就是睡在這一堆衣服之下。<br />\n<br />\n寮屋劏房租戶梁先生稱：「住房的大小、設施，當然不會有全部配套，一個人會有全部的空間，大部分都是數個人用同一廁所，有些甚至沒有廚房，只是人人拿著個電飯煲，啟動它，甚麼都是靠電飯煲。」<br />\n<br />\n鄰舍層面社區發展聯席，去年十月至今年三月訪問北區、大埔和荃灣等六個地區，97個住在寮屋區劏房、貨櫃屋及組合屋的租戶。<br />\n<br />\n近八成受訪住戶居住單位面積，由100平方呎以下至200平方呎，其中寮屋劏房面積的中位數，每戶為150平方呎。<br />\n<br />\n按此計算，調查指寮屋劏房的人均居住面積只有63平方呎，<span style=\"color: red;\">比懲教署的獨立囚室細</span>。<br />\n<br />\n鄰舍層面社區發展聯席代表王坤榮稱：「觀察到寮屋劏房數量有增加，好多過往是豬欄，或農舍改建成劏房，至於甚麼原因，他們見到『有價有市』，自然會非法或不非法將寮屋改建成劏房出租。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5aeefc78e60383605bebc409/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5aeefc78e60383605bebc409%2F&d=yrWxp8spTKOudE0FY6n35cn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6bf4ace3\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5aeefc78e60383605bebc409/</a>"},{"pid":"2a3c88ba95eed2955b5cc0eed27e52d655d474db","tid":655494,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"將來 坐監要不要交 市值租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3122d0f2e7bd3db8485c8847b1175c5fa3c278fb","tid":655494,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a3c88ba95eed2955b5cc0eed27e52d655d474db","tid":655494,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"將來 坐監要不要交 市值租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"赤柱地段租金肯定天價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b7d4b66f9e9071800d7af6ad0e81b0d002225e","tid":655494,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:33:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f5ac3b75c59418a05ed04af10949372be4f79af","tid":655494,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T15:48:59.000Z","msg":"冇人理樓豬，幫手推吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18599f9ab043cea74b05220af75eaba3912af52","tid":655494